	* src/: include/PT/Stitcher.h, hugin/PreviewPanel.cpp: added a
	  faster simple, copy ontop of eachother stitcher, for use in the
	  preview panel. Should be a lot faster than the old solution. Not
	  tested well yet..

2004-07-07 00:53  dangelo

	* src/: hugin/ImageCache.cpp, hugin/PreviewPanel.cpp,
	  include/PT/ImageTransforms.h, include/PT/Stitcher.h,
	  include/hugin/ImageCache.h, include/hugin/PreviewPanel.h: added
	  remap cache, speeds up preview panel A LOT the better seam line
	  calculation still takes a lot of time..  should offer a "quick
	  mode" that just copies the images over eachother.

