	  (removed many fixed sizes), there seemed to be many
	  unessecary layers of sizers in images/pano panel.	- uses new
	  Panorama model, resulted in massive code size reduction     -
	  drawback: not all features of the old code available	 - List
	  class replaced     - split List into a base class and specialized
	  classes for each layout.     - completely separate now. no more
	  ugly global variables for communication

	   - many other changes I forgot, I just want to commit the whole
	  thing now ;)

