	  src/hugin/xrc/data/searchfind.xpm, src/hugin/xrc/data/undo.xpm,
	  src/hugin/xrc/data/zoomin.xpm, src/hugin/xrc/data/zoomout.xpm,
	  src/include/PT/Panorama.h, src/include/hugin/CPEditorPanel.h,
	  src/include/hugin/huginApp.h, src/makefiles/Makefile.template,
	  src/makefiles/config.mk, src/makefiles/rules.mk: changes to the
	  build system:  o moved hugin application specific data (po files,
	  images etc)	 into the hugin subdir. I like this more than
	  linking it (doesn't work    on windows).   o locale_path is not
	  reset to "../po" to the config file all the time.   o hugin looks
	  for xrc (and their data) and po files under the current
	  directory. if they can't be found it checks locale_path and
	  xrc_path     from the config file / registry	 o added hand
	  written configure script. maybe its a good idea to	 create one
	  with autoconf with more checks.

